147
00:10:19,080 --> 00:10:20,549
Bapak diundang?

148
00:10:24,490 --> 00:10:25,590
Aku?

149
00:10:25,950 --> 00:10:29,120
Ini resital siswa.

150
00:10:29,120 --> 00:10:31,289
